txt.en: 'Our scouts could not have been wrong. The Uruk was injured. What fell magic restored it after it was so grievously wounded? Come, let us return with this news.'
A great leader amongst the Uruk from the White Hand was severely injured in an attack at Caras Geleden. You have been sent to finish the creature.
Defeat the injured White Hand war-leader
Defeat melee Uruk-hai of the White Hand ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
